Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to leave{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for dress rehearsal{\i0}\N{\i1}soon, Rarity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it finished yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel it needs a\Ncertain je ne sais quoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,appliques.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Appliques?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,sequins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sweetie Belle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I adore having you\Nhelp me, truly I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I got a\Nlittle carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I know how\Nimportant it is for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to finish this wardrobe in\Ntime for Sapphire Shores
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and her backup dancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is without a doubt my\Nmost prestigious order ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Sapphire Shores\Nis THE Pony of Pop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and her Equestria-wide tour\Nlaunches in Canterlot next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which means she must have these\Noutfits by day after tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But is there time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Barely. But I work\Nwell under pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. As long as I stay\Ncalm I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe you could check the\Nstitching and finish the buttons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,on the dresses I made for me,\NApplebloom and Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want them\Nto look perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think I need\Nyour expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you've been so much help to\Nme, how could I possibly say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you need them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For the opening\Nnight of our show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sweetie Belle darling,\NI'm behind as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose if I got a few\Nmore ponies to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you, thank\Nyou, thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best sister ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The dresses are\Nright over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My goodness girls,{\i0}\N{\i1}it's time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the audience is\Nalmost fully seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Rarity\Nstill isn't here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been very\Nbusy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can she\Nstill not be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's known about\Nthis for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, she has known about\Nthis for weeks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept meaning to ask\Nher; I really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I worked so\Nhard on this play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote it especially\Nfor the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I directed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that this is\Nreally my time to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,doing something\Ncompletely myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and I really wanted\Nto keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But we wanted everything\Nto be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All our friends came\Nout to see it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Places!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm here. I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon for\Ncutting it so close,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I made some improvements\Nto your original design
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had a terrible time\Nwith these froofy sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is for the first play{\i0}\N{\i1}you ever wrote, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made quite certain\Nit came out just so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Places? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forsooth and anon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cometh forthwith{\i0}\N{\i1}and post haste{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with glad tidings, m'ladies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A standing ovation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be like a dream\Ncome true for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,huh, Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, can you imagine\Nif this show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is how you got\Nyour cutie mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you think\Nyou'd get it for:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}writing, directing or acting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a whole lobby\Nfull of friends waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to shower us with\Nadoration and praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to be gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Classy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are! The\Nstars of the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You may tell us how\Nmuch you loved it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Line forms here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your sisters\Nwould have loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Would have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sorry but they\Nhad to go help Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,get Sapphire Shores'\Nwardrobe ready
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to take to Canterlot\Nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Rarity fell\Nway behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, cheer up. The\Nshow was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you some punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At least everypony else who\Nwas able to stay loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you all like best?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The writing, the\Ndirecting or the acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I loved\Nthe dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked some of\Nthose lines you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Which ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but you were wearing\Na pink taffeta dress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with lots of chiffon\Nwhen you said them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo-whee, that\Noutfit was a dazzler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked that one almost as much\Nas the one with the lacy trim
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the embroidered\Ncuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was a nice one, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anypony here\Nwho remembers anything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about the play\Nbesides the dresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this is\None headpiece?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This marvelous extravagance\Nis the creme de la creme
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the entire wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But, alas, without this key\Nhidden stitch, it's just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to think of a\Nclassy way to say "big bummer".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! Now perhaps we can all at\Nlast take a moment to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever's the\Nmatter, Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't the play\Ngo all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Was something amiss with\Nthe dresses I made you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. They were perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the whole problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um. I think maybe I'll go\Ntake that moment to relax now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure do feel like relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right behind ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ooh, what amazing\Ndresses."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, how I loved the dresses."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ooh, dresses dresses\Ndresses dresses."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so they\Ndid like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You had me worried,\Nyou silly filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You did this on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing the spotlight\Nlike you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fifth birthday\Nparty all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act like you\Ndon't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you trying\Nto prove
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a better\Nactress than me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, if I did\Nanything to upset you then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit you made those\Ndresses too good on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they were\Nsupposed to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Good. Not\Njaw-dropping amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I only tried to do what\NI thought you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,HA!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr. I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything I put\Nup with all week long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sweetie Belle,\Nget me some red ribbon."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"No that's not red,\Nthat's cherry."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"No that's not red,\Nthat's cinnamon."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For Pete's sake, it's all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I should probably\Ngo talk to her, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At least Sapphire Shores\Nwon't be all like,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ooh, who fetched you\Nthat red ribbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't care about\Nanything else you made;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all I care about is that\NAMAZING RED RIBBON."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps waiting would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can't even sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy now, big sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there was a way I could\Ntake back all the work I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the winner of Best\NWriter-Director-Actor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in an Awesome Play\NPut On by a Pony
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and Her Awesome Best\NFriends goes to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sweetie Belle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to\Nruin everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ENOUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!\NIt's really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You just rescued me from a\Nmaniacal laughing Rarity Cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you're\Ngoing through, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I too have a sister who often\Nshines more brightly than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And with this I have struggled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Come back! Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Luna! Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fifth\Nbirthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I decided to make{\i0}\N{\i1}a grand entrance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made myself all beautiful,{\i0}\N{\i1}just like my big sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally I was perfect, and\Nthen went to the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to enter like the\Nbelle of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I finally came{\i0}\N{\i1}out of my room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I found the party{\i0}\N{\i1}going on without me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I kept posing at\Nthe top of the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting to be noticed,\Nbut all I heard was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These party favors\Nare the coolest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Made them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course you'll\Nall want cake, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the greatest, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who needs a birthday girl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when you've got the birthday{\i0}\N{\i1}girl's amazing big sister?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I learned\Nnever try to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with my big sister around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps you didn't\Nhave the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said\Nyou understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Sweetie Belle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be\Nalong at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we get out of here before\Nwe all keel over from boredom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony's gonna come to another\None of her parties
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,after this fiasco.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go. You'll miss out on\Nthe... party favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to save them\Ntill the end but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These party favors\Nare the coolest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Where'd you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I made them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, you'll all\Nwant cake, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who needs a birthday girl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,when you've got the birthday\Ngirl's amazing big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these things were\NSweetie Belle's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just assisted\Nwith the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Rarity wasn't trying\Nto steal the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She was trying to save my party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I hem the cloaks\Nnow or wait until I'm there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hem them now but\NI might have to redo them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I wait until I'm\Nin Canterlot to hem them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapphire Shores might not get\Nthe best first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. This must've happened\Nearlier tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapphire Shores is\Nsuch a big star
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and such a stickler\Nfor details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What if everything's\Nnot perfect enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny, I thought I was\Nthe only one who got worried
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Buck up, Rarity;\Nstop this foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done your best and\Nleft nothing to chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's needed now\Nis a good night's rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope everything goes all\Nright for her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. How curious you\Nshould say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go. Go see what\Nthe future holds
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if you fail to rein in your\Nworst instincts as I once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The crème de la crème.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The piece de resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The headdress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I made\Na mistake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked and\Nrechecked everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This couldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about that, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. You must believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Always check and recheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who all wants to\Nhear a funny story
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,about my ex-costume\Ndesigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Check, recheck and\Nrecheck and recheck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna,\Ncan you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me a dress, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away. You know I\Ndon't do that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake me up,\NPrincess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake me up! Wake me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The boxes. Gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She left for Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is for you two to\Ndistract Rarity long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to put the stitch back\Nin without her noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're not too late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're going\Nto see Sapphire Shores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a huge fan.\NI know all her songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Get Your Pony On".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, that's one of\Nmy favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't a trip to{\i0}\N{\i1}see Sapphire Shores.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trip to save my sister\Nfrom a horrible future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Serves Her Right".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity doesn't\Ndeserve that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No. "Serves Her Right"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is another one of\NSapphire Shores' songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You seriously didn't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you listen to her music?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer showtunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five, six{\i0}\N{\i1}seven eight, ba-bam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fabulous! Magnifique!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time.\NFrom the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not embarrass me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of my favorite\Ndesigner this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And a one-two-three-four!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sapphire Shores'\Ndesigner's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to believe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, the only thing I have to\Ndo is make sure Sapphire Shores
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't get interrupted\Nall day by fans like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's how I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You rocked it, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some water\Nand be back in ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, come on up here and\Nshow me what you brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapphire wants to see\Nit and to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get in there. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}OK, then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Liking what I see so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So is this the whole shebang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I saved\Nthe best for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta see this\Nwith the cinnamon ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good! This is\Njust a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, no. This\Nis very much real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Luna, I wish none\Nof this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I know how\Nyou can even improve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know what in the\Nwide wide realm of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,this stunt of yours is all\Nabout, and I want to know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how\Nimportant this job is to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was upset at you for stealing\N{\i1}the spotlight from me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,at the play,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so I pulled out the center\Nstitch to the headpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so it would fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I realized I didn't\Nwant your future to be ruined
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,forever and ever so I\Ncame back to change it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,before it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So here it is; it's all fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me; Sapphire Shores\Nis going to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, this isn't\Ngoing to work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to my\Nlevel of success
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,without learning\Nto read the signs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and this situation has bad\Nluck written all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you'll\Nabsolutely adore the headdress
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My, it is attractive, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the stitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Real close.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I'll be.{\i0}\N{\i1}It's a dolphin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my lucky animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They swim with me in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever did you come up\Nwith the idea for a dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it just came to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I got jealous\Nabout those dresses;
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know now that you were\Nonly trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Sweetie, I\Nforgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never did get\Nto see your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Any chance I could catch\Nan encore performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the play\Nwas all that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest? The costumes\Nwere the best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Awwww.
